[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0716","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0716.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0917","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer Preloader ActiveX 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 浏览器使用的 Preloader ActiveX 控件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者可通过诱导用户访问恶意网页，利用该 ActiveX 控件读取目标系统上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows 系统中 Internet Explorer 浏览器支持的版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害较大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0917"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.540","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-018 提供的补丁（对应 KB231452），该补丁会彻底移除存在风险的 Preloader ActiveX 控件。如无法安装补丁，可在注册表中为 Preloader ActiveX 控件设置 Kill Bit（CLSID: {0000-0000-...}）以禁用该控件。鉴于 Internet Explorer 已停止安全支持，建议升级到现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）作为根本解决方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231452","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-018"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0716.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0806","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0806.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0802","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"tags. Let me provide the final answer.<value>Internet Explorer 5 的收藏夹功能在处理网站提供的自定义图标时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可构造特制的畸形图标文件，当用户使用 IE 5 访问包含恶意图标的网页时触发缓冲区溢出，从而在用户系统上以当前用户权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98 平台上的 Internet Explorer 5 浏览器，CVSS 评分 7.6，危害等级高危。Microsoft 已在 MS99-018 安全公告中发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0802"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.283","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-018 提供的 Internet Explorer 5 更新补丁（KB231450），或升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 2 及以上版本。当前 IE5 已停止支持，建议升级至 Microsoft Edge 或使用其他现代浏览器以避免更多安全风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231450","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-018"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0806.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0726","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0726.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0927","title":"Gordano NTMail Web目录遍历漏洞","description":"Gordano NTMail 4.2 Web 邮件系统存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 URL 中注入 ../ 序列可绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞无需身份认证即可利用，攻击条件简单，影响运行 NTMail 4.2 版本的服务器系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0927"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.713","remediation":"立即升级 NTMail 至 4.2 以上已修复路径遍历漏洞的安全版本，或联系 Gordano 厂商获取针对该漏洞的安全补丁。在 IIS Web 服务器前端部署 URLScan 工具，配置过滤规则拦截包含连续 \"..\" 的 URL 请求，并对 NTMail Web 虚拟目录启用 NTFS 权限限制，确保 Web 进程账户仅能访问必要目录。由于该产品已停止维护，强烈建议迁移至现代受支持的邮件服务器（如 Exchange Server）以消除长期安全风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD05261999.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/279","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19222"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0726.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0496","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0496.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0771","title":"Compaq Management Agents 及 Survey Utility 目录遍历漏洞","description":"Compaq（现HP）管理代理的Web组件存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的Web管理接口发送包含\"..\"特殊字符的HTTP请求，绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞影响Compaq Client Management Agents 3.70/4.0、Insight Management Agents 4.21 A至4.30 A、Server Management Agents 4.23等多个版本，攻击者无需认证即可利用，可能导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0771"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-05-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止支持的 Compaq/HP Management Agents 及 Survey Utility 服务，在受影响服务器上卸载该软件并禁用相关 Web 端口（默认 2301）。如业务必须使用，应升级至 HP 后续支持的 Systems Insight Manager 版本，并在 Web 服务器配置中禁用目录遍历及父路径访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0771","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19225"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0496.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1308","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1308.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0920","title":"华盛顿大学 IMAP 软件包 pop2d 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"University of Washington IMAP 软件包中的 pop-2d POP 守护进程存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标系统发送特制的 FOLD 命令触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出并获取系统权限。该漏洞影响 IMAP 软件包 4.4 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。目前该漏洞已有公开的利用代码。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0920"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-26","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 UW IMAP 软件包至 4.5 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，建议禁用 pop-2d 服务（POP2 协议已过时），改用 POP3 或 IMAP 协议，并在网络边界防火墙限制对 109/TCP 端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/283","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19226"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19226"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1308.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0539","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0539.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0803","title":"IBM AIX eNetwork Firewall 不安全临时文件创建漏洞","description":"IBM AIX eNetwork Firewall 3.2 及 3.3 版本中的 fwluser 脚本存在不安全临时文件创建漏洞。具有本地访问权限的攻击者可通过符号链接（symlink）攻击，诱使脚本以提升的权限向任意系统文件写入恶意内容，从而覆盖关键配置文件或获取更高权限。该漏洞需攻击者拥有本地账户，利用难度较低，影响系统完整性与可用性。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0803"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.407","remediation":"tags.<value>IBM AIX eNetwork Firewall 3.2/3.3 已停止支持且 IBM 未对 APAR IR39562 发布正式补丁，建议立即迁移至受支持的防火墙产品。如必须继续使用，应限制本地用户 shell 访问权限，将 /tmp 目录以 nosuid 选项挂载并确保粘滞位生效，同时修改 fwluser 脚本使用 mktemp 命令替代可预测临时文件名以防止符号链接劫持。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92765973207648&w=2","http://www.osvdb.org/962","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19229"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0539.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1102","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1102.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1414","title":"IBM Netfinity Remote Control 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM Netfinity Remote Control（远程控制软件）1.0 存在权限提升漏洞。该软件的任务管理器以系统级权限运行，本地攻击者可通过任务管理器启动任意程序，从而获得管理员权限。攻击者只需拥有本地访问权限即可利用此漏洞，无需身份认证。该漏洞影响 IBM Remote Control Software 1.0 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1414"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:23.410","remediation":"立即升级 IBM Netfinity Remote Control 至最新版本或迁移至 IBM Director 系列管理工具。如无法升级，限制仅允许受信任管理员账户登录系统，并在本地安全策略中禁用进程管理器对非管理员的访问权限。同时建议使用防火墙限制远程管理端口的访问来源 IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92765856706547&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92902484317769&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/284","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19227"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1102.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0478","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0478.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0762","title":"Netscape Communicator 浏览器信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 浏览器在处理 HTML TITLE 标签中嵌入的 JavaScript 代码时存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过诱导用户访问恶意网页，利用 \"about\" 协议获取浏览器内部信息，包括浏览历史、配置数据等敏感内容。该漏洞影响 Netscape Communicator 4.x 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，但需要用户交互配合。此漏洞 CVSS 评分 2.6，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0762"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.337","remediation":"升级到 Netscape Communicator 4.73 或更高版本，该版本修复了 TITLE 标签中 JavaScript 可访问 about 协议信息的问题。由于 Netscape Communicator 已停止维护，建议立即迁移至现代浏览器（如 Firefox、Chrome），并在迁移前禁用浏览器 JavaScript 功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0762"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0478.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0728","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0728.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0928","title":"SmartDesk WebSuite 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"SmartDesk WebSuite 2.1 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送超长 URL 触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务拒绝（DoS）。该漏洞源于程序未对用户输入的 URL 长度进行有效边界检查，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，影响 SmartDesk WebSuite 2.1 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0928"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.837","remediation":"升级 SmartDesk WebSuite 至厂商修复版本，或应用厂商提供的安全补丁。如产品已停止维护，建议立即迁移至受支持的企业级 Web 服务平台。临时缓解措施包括在反向代理或 WAF 层限制 URL 长度不超过 2048 字节，并过滤超长请求中的恶意载荷。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/278","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19221"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0728.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1096","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1096.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1393","title":"Apple Mac OS PowerBook 密码安全绕过漏洞","description":"Apple PowerBook 笔记本电脑的\"密码安全\"控制面板存在安全绕过漏洞。具有物理访问权限的攻击者可通过使用紧急启动盘引导系统，绕过正常操作系统安全机制，利用磁盘编辑工具修改正常情况下不可访问的 aaaaaaaAPWD 文件中的密码开关或密码内容，从而完全绕过设备密码保护。该漏洞影响 Apple Mac OS 8.5 及 8.6 版本，CVSS v2 评分 4.6，攻击者需物理接触目标设备，但无需任何认证即可获取系统的完全访问权限，导致机密性、完整性和可用性均受部分影响。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1393"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-21","updated":"1999-05-21","remediation":"在 Mac OS 8.5/8.6 上启用 Open Firmware 密码保护，防止从外部启动磁盘引导系统；将启动顺序设置为仅内置硬盘，并设置固件密码阻止未授权修改。同时加强物理安全措施，使用防盗锁固定设备，防止攻击者获得物理访问权限。升级到 Mac OS 9 或更高版本可从根本上消除此漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1393.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1393","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1393.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1393.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gh96-8q4m-h947/GHSA-gh96-8q4m-h947.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/532/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1393.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000643.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1096.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0312","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0312.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0715","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 远程访问服务电话簿条目缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 远程访问服务（RAS）客户端在处理电话簿条目时存在未经检查的缓冲区，攻击者可通过向 RAS 客户端提供特制的畸形电话簿条目触发缓冲区溢出，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。该漏洞影响 RAS 客户端而非服务器，攻击者需要具有添加或修改电话簿条目的权限方可利用，无法通过远程直接利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0715"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-20","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"安装微软安全公告 MS99-016 提供的补丁程序，升级 Windows NT 4.0 RAS 客户端至修补版本，限制电话簿文件的 ACL 权限仅允许授权用户修改，防止非授权用户通过畸形电话簿条目触发缓冲区溢出。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ230677","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-016","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19211","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0715.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0715","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0715.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0715.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w83x-7v2j-2q4m/GHSA-w83x-7v2j-2q4m.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0715.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0312.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0686","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0686.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0765","title":"SGI IRIX midikeys 本地任意文件修改漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.5.4 系统中的 midikeys 程序存在权限处理缺陷，本地攻击者可通过文本编辑器利用该程序以提升的权限修改任意系统文件，从而实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.5.4 及可能的相关版本，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，无需网络远程即可触发，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0765"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:00.710","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 安全公告 19990501-01-A 提供的补丁，或从 ftp://patches.sgi.com/support/free/security/advisories/19990501-01-A 获取。如无法打补丁，可移除 midikeys 程序的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/midikeys）或直接删除该程序作为临时缓解措施。SGI IRIX 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/262","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19210","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e6863af1ae3bb1cd8c56c1f1aac61d836661ac74/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0765.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0765","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0765.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0765.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-4wg8-h27h-453j/GHSA-4wg8-h27h-453j.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0765.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c5545578-048e-4acc-97a2-487c23d98355.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--c5545578-048e-4acc-97a2-487c23d98355.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0686.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0886","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0886.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1031","title":"Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 counter.exe 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 版本的 counter.exe 组件存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向该程序发送超长参数，触发缓冲区处理异常，导致目标程序挂起（hang），无法正常响应后续请求。该漏洞仅需网络可达即可触发，无需身份认证，攻击门槛低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1031"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:33.700","remediation":"升级 Behold Web Page Counter 至 2.71 或更高版本。如厂商已停止维护，建议部署 Web 应用防火墙（WAF）过滤超长请求参数，或在 Web 服务器层面对 counter.exe 的输入参数长度进行限制（如限制 URL 参数不超过 1024 字节），亦可迁移至其他受支持的网站计数器替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92713790426690&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92707671717292&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/267","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1031","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1031.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hmhc-wx7p-hg6x/GHSA-hmhc-wx7p-hg6x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/267/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1031.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153400_153500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0886.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0885","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0885.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1030","title":"Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Behold Software Web Page Counter 2.70 的 counter.exe 组件存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送以 %0A（换行符）结尾的恶意 HTTP 请求，触发计数器日志写入异常，产生无效记录导致访问冲突，从而使程序崩溃挂起。该漏洞影响 Web Page Counter 2.70 版本，攻击者无需任何认证即可远程实施攻击，危害程度中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1030"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-19","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该软件已停止维护，建议立即停止使用 Behold Web Page Counter 2.70，替换为现代网页计数器方案。若必须继续使用，在 Web 服务器（如 IIS 或 Apache）反向代理层过滤包含 %0A 的畸形请求，阻止对 counter.exe 的异常访问。定期审查日志文件是否存在畸形条目并清理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92713790426690&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92707671717292&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/267","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19212"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0885.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0315","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0315.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0716","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 帮助文件工具缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 的帮助文件处理程序（WinHelp）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，当用户打开一个特制的 .hlp 帮助文件时，可触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致任意代码执行。攻击者可通过诱导用户访问恶意网页或打开包含恶意帮助文件的邮件附件来利用此漏洞。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 所有 SP 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0716"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.460","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-015 提供的补丁（KB 文章 Q231605），该补丁可阻止通过畸形帮助文件执行任意代码。由于 Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持，建议升级到 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016+ 等受支持版本。临时缓解措施：限制用户对 WINNT\\help 目录的写入权限，仅允许管理员修改该目录下的帮助文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231605","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-015","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19209","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0716.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0716.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0716","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0716.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0716.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wv77-33q2-xmgf/GHSA-wv77-33q2-xmgf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d026